02753 static inline
02754 CSL_Status NAND_getSetup(CSL_EmifHandle      hEmif,
02755                          CSL_AsyncConfig     *getAsynchConfig,
02756                          CSL_NandConfig      *getNandConfig)
02757 {
02758     volatile ioport Uint16    *asyncCfg0Addr;
02759     volatile ioport Uint16    *asyncCfg1Addr;
02760     Int16         loopCount;
02761     Uint16        tempVal;
02762     CSL_Status    result;
02763 
02764     result = CSL_SOK;
02765 
02766     if((hEmif != NULL) && (getAsynchConfig != NULL))
02767     {
02768         getNandConfig->nandWidth    = hEmif->nandWidth;
02769         getNandConfig->nandPageSize = hEmif->nandPageSize;
02770         getNandConfig->emifOpMode   = hEmif->emifOpMode;
02771         getNandConfig->nandType     = hEmif->nandType;
02772 
02773         /* Get the chip select */
02774         tempVal = CSL_FEXTR(hEmif->regs->NANDFCR,
02775                             CSL_EMIF_NANDFCR_CS5_USE_NAND_SHIFT,
02776                             CSL_EMIF_NANDFCR_CS2_USE_NAND_SHIFT);
02777 
02778         loopCount = -1;
02779         while(tempVal)
02780         {
02781             loopCount++;
02782             tempVal = (tempVal >> 1);
02783         }
02784 
02785         getAsynchConfig->chipSelect =  (CSL_EmifChipSelect)loopCount;
02786 
02787         /* Get async wait config register setting */
02788         switch(getAsynchConfig->chipSelect)
02789         {
02790             case CSL_EMIF_CS2:
02791                 /* CS2 */
02792 //              getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitPin =                            \
02793 //                          (CSL_EmifWaitPin)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR2,            \
02794 //                                                 EMIF_AWCCR2_CS2_WAIT);
02795 
02796                 asyncCfg0Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS2CR1);
02797                 asyncCfg1Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS2CR2);
02798                 break;
02799 
02800             case CSL_EMIF_CS3:
02801                 /* CS3 */
02802 //              getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitPin =                            \
02803 //                          (CSL_EmifWaitPin)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR2,            \
02804 //                                                 EMIF_AWCCR2_CS3_WAIT);
02805 
02806                 asyncCfg0Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS3CR1);
02807                 asyncCfg1Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS3CR2);
02808                 break;
02809 
02810             case CSL_EMIF_CS4:
02811                 /* CS4 */
02812 //              getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitPin =                            \
02813 //                          (CSL_EmifWaitPin)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR2,            \
02814 //                                                 EMIF_AWCCR2_CS4_WAIT);
02815 
02816                 asyncCfg0Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS4CR1);
02817                 asyncCfg1Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS4CR2);
02818                 break;
02819 
02820             case CSL_EMIF_CS5:
02821                 /* CS5 */
02822 //              getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitPin =                            \
02823 //                          (CSL_EmifWaitPin)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR2,            \
02824 //                                                 EMIF_AWCCR2_CS5_WAIT);
02825 
02826                 asyncCfg0Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS5CR1);
02827                 asyncCfg1Addr = &(hEmif->regs->ACS5CR2);
02828                 break;
02829 
02830             default:
02831                 break;
02832         }
02833 
02834         /* Get the wait polarity */
02835 //      getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitPol =                                     \
02836 //                      (CSL_EmifWaitPol)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR2,               \
02837                                                 EMIF_AWCCR2_WP0);
02838 
02839         /* Get the extended wait cycles */
02840 //      getAsynchConfig->asyncWaitCfg->waitCycles = CSL_FEXT(hEmif->regs->AWCCR1,    \
02841 //                                                         EMIF_AWCCR1_MEWC);
02842 
02843 
02844         /* Get async configuration register values */
02845         /* Get strobe mode select bit */
02846         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->selectStrobe = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,           \
02847                                                          EMIF_ACS2CR2_SS);
02848         /* Get extended wait mode bit */
02849         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->ewMode = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,                 \
02850                                                    EMIF_ACS2CR2_EW);
02851         /* Get write srobe setup cycles */
02852         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->w_setup = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,                \
02853                                                     EMIF_ACS2CR2_WSETUP);
02854         /* Get write duration cycles */
02855         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->w_strobe = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,               \
02856                                                      EMIF_ACS2CR2_WSTROBE);
02857         /* Get write hold cycles */
02858         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->w_hold = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,                 \
02859                                                    EMIF_ACS2CR2_WHOLD);
02860         /* Get read strobe setup cycles */
02861         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->r_setup = ((CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg1Addr,              \
02862                                             EMIF_ACS2CR2_RSETUPMSB) << 3) |        \
02863                                             (CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg0Addr,              \
02864                                             EMIF_ACS2CR1_RSETUPLSB) & 0x7));
02865         /* Get read strobe duration cycles */
02866         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->r_strobe = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg0Addr,               \
02867                                                      EMIF_ACS2CR1_RSTROBE);
02868         /* Get read strobe hold cycles */
02869         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->r_hold = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg0Addr,                 \
02870                                                    EMIF_ACS2CR1_RHOLD);
02871         /* Get turn around cycles */
02872         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->turnAround = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg0Addr,             \
02873                                                        EMIF_ACS2CR1_TA);
02874         /* Get asynchronous memory size */
02875         getAsynchConfig->asyncCfg->aSize = CSL_FEXT(*asyncCfg0Addr,                  \
02876                                                   EMIF_ACS2CR1_ASIZE);
02877 
02878         /* emif Byte access */
02879         getAsynchConfig->emifAccess =                                                \
02880                   (CSL_EmifAccess)CSL_FEXT(hEmif->sysCtrlRegs->ESCR,           \
02881                                                SYS_ESCR_BYTEMODE);
02882     }
02883     else
02884     {
02885         result = CSL_ESYS_INVPARAMS;
02886     }
02887 
02888     return(result);
02889 }
